column1:
:::ro.com.lge.mada version gms_7.0 detected doesn't match to the one gms_3.1 entered
Test Case Description:
1) adb shell getprop "ro.com.lge.mada" should match selected gms_version
Pass: if selected gms_version in AutoQa App match
Fail: Otherwise
*If "ro.com.lge.mada" is Empty
